## 模块权限配置

### permission_level 含义

| 级别 | 说明 | 适用模块 |
|------|------|---------|
| `restricted` | 仅指定团队可读写，所有操作审计 | XPVehicleSDK |
| `team_managed` | 归属团队可读写，其他团队只读 | XPBusiness_* |
| `public` | 全员可读，有权限者可写 | XPBase_* |

### YAML 配置示例

```yaml
permission_config:
  rbac_enabled: true
  cache_ttl_seconds: 300    # 权限缓存5分钟
  audit_enabled: true       # 开启审计日志

  roles:
    senior_architect:
      description: "高级架构师"
      permissions:
        - "vehicle_sdk:read"
        - "vehicle_sdk:write"
        - "business_modules:read"
        - "business_modules:write"
        - "base_modules:read"
        - "base_modules:write"
        - "ai_assist:all_modules"
        - "admin:system_config"

    vehicle_team_member:
      description: "车控团队成员"
      permissions:
        - "vehicle_sdk:read"
        - "vehicle_sdk:write"
        - "ai_assist:vehicle_modules"
        - "base_modules:read"

    business_developer:
      description: "业务开发人员"
      permissions:
        - "business_modules:read"
        - "business_modules:write"
        - "base_modules:read"
        - "base_modules:write"
        - "ai_assist:business_modules"

  module_permissions:
    XPVehicleSDK:
      permission_level: "restricted"
      owners: ["vehicle-team", "senior-architect"]
      ai_restrictions:
        - "require_human_review_for_core_apis"
        - "audit_all_ai_generated_changes"

    "XPBusiness_*":          # 通配符匹配所有业务模块
      permission_level: "team_managed"
      owners: ["business-team"]

    "XPBase_*":              # 通配符匹配所有基础模块
      permission_level: "public"
      owners: ["platform-team"]
```

